News of htmlview

* 0.7.0 (2015-03-24)
  * fix build error when --prefix is not specified
    [GitHub#3][Reported by @tliron]
  * update install instruction
    [GitHub#4,#6][Reported by @tliron]
  * fix linking against invalid modable module
    [GitHub#5][Reported by @tliron]

* 0.6.0 (2015-03-24)
  * clean up build process

* 0.5.0 (2013-05-02)
  * supported windows
  * added Travis-CI integration

* 0.4.0 (2013-02-18)

  * fix a bug that conflicts other plugin
  * use font size setting from sylpheedrc
  * support GtkHTML

* 0.3.0 (2012-08-01)

  * depends on show_attach_tab option for rendering HTML
  * add 'Show HTML as default' option

* 0.2.1 (2012-06-30)

  * fix grab focus problem

* 0.2.0 (2012-06-28)

  * added options(enable-private-browsing,auto-load-images,enable-scripts)

* 0.1.0 (2012-06-24)

  * initial release
